pageProduct.name: Wagner Vegan Hemp Seed Oil 1000mg 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Hemp Seed oil capsule

Common Uses

Hemp seed Oil hs been extracted from the seeds of the Hemp plant (Cannabis sativa).  Seeds have been cold pressed and not exposed to artificial heat at any stage of the extraction process

Ingredients

Each capsule provides:
Hemp Seed Oil 1000mg
Equiv Oleic acid (Omega 9) 60mg
Equiv. Linoleic acid (Omega 6) 450mg
Equiv a-Linolenic Acid (Omega 3) 140mg

 

Directions

Take 2 capsules with food or as directed by your healthcare professional.
